text: Amangildino () is a rural locality (a village) in Amangildinsky Selsoviet, Uchalinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 110 as of 2010. There are 3 streets. == Geography == It is located 65 km from Uchaly, 5 km from Malokazakkulovo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Uchalinsky District
title: Amangildino, Uchalinsky District, Republic of Bashkortostan
